    "Although minor variations exist, they remain within an acceptable range, indicating that users need not devote much effort to tuning the key.",
    "Additionally, the empirical results further strengthen our claim that the key-dependent variability in the frequency-domain representation does not substantially affect watermark distortion or detectability.Multi-key scenarios.",
